,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"以毒攻毒"},{"pid":"5702d49e91d680d9815dda84e75c802130d928a0","tid":1810711,"uid":2757,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"食染咗非洲豬瘟嘅豬肉，以毒攻毒"},{"pid":"11999935bf5f5d7cdbda47a5e54b4c52e2143878","tid":1810711,"uid":315545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"量子波動解毒法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c85b3e8cf94d95f088f71095c2e2788c4eff38e","tid":1810711,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"問陳云根啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac8c122a3861f3621f287178d4cb92b03a44a7e","tid":1810711,"uid":155902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"每日朝早黃昏向北京朝拜並用蝗語大叫 &quot;習維尼萬歲&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf9a51ea0d3bce2068a75c109be063af593462f","tid":1810711,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"華夏文化, 可以笑死： <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：Inconvenient truth, 不大好意思告訴你的真相，因為告訴你，我會被繼續迫害，搞到窮途末路。關於愛滋病、沙士之類的現代病。<br />\n我在德國遊學期間，認識一些研究微生物學及病毒的生物學家，他們告訴我這件事。<br />\n關於愛滋病。<br />\n在野獸或人體的愛滋病一直存在，直至人類辨認了病毒及嘗試發明治療方法的時候，愛滋病成了疾病，很多藥廠發財了，很多研究所開業了，很多學者升官了，很多人病了，避孕袋和塑膠醫療手套有新的銷路了，很多同性戀者受歧視了，同性戀者成為弱勢，要搞結婚平權了。<br />\n感染了愛滋病的人，在告訴他驗證了愛滋病之前是沒事的，醫生告訴他之後，就會發病，嘗試治療之後，就會死亡。<br />\n我相信那些生物學家的講法。至於沙士、禽流感這些病，也是一樣。你不理會它，它只是惡性的流感而已，一年半載就會被人體適應，而其實他們一直存在與某些人類之中而相安無事。<br />\n我講出這些真相，一定被人攻擊，注定一世無運行，窮過鬼。<br />\n我在2003年沙士的時候，我也勸告政府毋須理會，但結果呢？香港發現了病毒和治療法，也死人最多。很多人升官發財，機場也將作狀的檢疫恆久化，不斷侵擾人權。之後，我被逼離開政府，這只是其中一個原因&mdash;&mdash;我阻止政府部門膨脹，我阻止人升官發財。"},{"pid":"aac85dc8b068843af3f1ffc65c10d984f2416a81","tid":1810711,"uid":76674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c85b3e8cf94d95f088f71095c2e2788c4eff38e","tid":1810711,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"問陳云根啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"條傻尻話唔洗醫"},{"pid":"ff51a0e4384c7b9e5f07a524bef5b9008bad20ab","tid":1810711,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:20:12.000Z","msg":"性交轉菌"},{"pid":"f55e1c57f971b1de5885d24a01e5d5cfd83c0986","tid":1810711,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aac85dc8b068843af3f1ffc65c10d984f2416a81","tid":1810711,"uid":76674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c85b3e8cf94d95f088f71095c2e2788c4eff38e","tid":1810711,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"問陳云根啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"條傻尻話唔洗醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"屌佢條廢老, 唔即日叫全部熱狗+青山派, 一齊搭高鐵去武漢活禽街市, 拍片直播食嘢味？<br />\n<br />\n阿年大挑戰 X 陳云根<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fdb3a5eafb985b58ecfe08c1f95ccc1cd85353","tid":1810711,"uid":69334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"武漢有個親戚試左蘇炸曱甴真係醫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好揚出去，缺貨就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立  唯一出路</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc30699f25f54b408f84421aa00a11f60771602","tid":1810711,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:23:16.000Z","msg":"煲狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee654d9b39dd7979d55